DATABASE|btf5_40|B-Tree Filer 5.40 - B-Tree DataBase Toolkit for BP7|TurboPower Software||B-Tree Filer v.5.40. B-Tree DataBase Toolkit. Supports DOS / Windows / DPMI / Netware / IPX / SPX. Full Pas/Asm sources|database b-tree binary tree bp7|<pre>          List of files distributed with B-Tree Filer 5.40<br><br>FILER disk<br>----------------<br>read.me           - news to update the printed manual<br>packing.lst       - this list of files<br>lharc.exe         - dearchiving program for LZH files<br>fastupd.540       - changes from previous version to this one<br>upgrade.exe       - program to upgrade Filer 5.0x programs to<br>                    5.21 or later<br>filer.upg         - substitution file used by UPGRADE.EXE<br>printdoc.exe      - program to paginate and print text files<br>filer.lzh         - archive containing B-Tree Filer single user<br>                    source code<br>  basesupp.pas        DOS/Windows compatibility unit<br>  bigsort.pas         sorting demonstration program<br>  browser.inc           included in browser.pas<br>  browser.pas         file browsing unit<br>  btdefine.inc        conditional defines affecting all units<br>  convert.pas         shows how to convert Database Toolbox data<br>                      to Filer<br>  dbox.upg            substitution file for DatabaseToolbox<br>  emsheap.cfg           included in emsheap.pas<br>  emsheap.pas         EMS heap manager unit<br>  emssupp.pas         low level EMS support unit<br>  errors              listing of all Filer error codes<br>  example.pas         single-user fileblock example routines<br>  filer.cfg           configuration constants for filer.pas<br>  filer.inc             included in filer.pas<br>  filer.mak           make file for single user B-Tree Filer<br>  filer.pas           the main fileblock management unit<br>  fixtovar.pas        unit to convert fixed length records to<br>                      variable length<br>  isambase.inc          included in filer.pas<br>  isamlow.inc           included in filer.pas<br>  isamtool.pas        miscellaneous routines supporting filer unit<br>  isamwork.inc          included in filer.pas<br>  iscompat.pas        version 5.0x backwards compatibility unit<br>                      for filer<br><br>  msort.pas           merge sort unit<br>  msortems.inc          included in msort.pas<br>  msortinf.inc          included in msort.pas<br>  netdemo.pas         filer demonstration program (depends on<br>                      Turbo Professional)<br>  numkeys.asm           assembly language for numkeys.obj<br>  numkeys.obj           linked into numkeys.pas<br>  numkeys.pas         numeric keys unit<br>  rebuild.pas         fileblock rebuilding unit<br>  reorg.pas           fileblock reorganization unit<br>  simpdemo.pas        filer demonstration program (standalone)<br>  tpalloc.pas         heap allocation unit for blocks &gt;64K<br>  tpcmd.pas           command processing unit used by browser.pas<br>  vrcompat.pas        version 5.0x backwards compatibility unit<br>                      for vrec<br>  vrebuild.pas        vrec fileblock rebuilding unit<br>  vrec.pas            variable length record support unit<br>  vreorg.pas          vrec fileblock reorganization unit<br><br>DEMO/HELP disk<br>----------------<br>netdemo.exe       - precompiled version of netdemo demonstration<br>                    program<br>address.dat       - data file for netdemo<br>address.ix        - address file for netdemo<br>bigsort.exe       - precompiled version of bigsort demonstration<br>                    program<br>btfhelp.lzh       - archive containing help text and popup help<br>                    utility<br>  pophelp.exe         popup help utility<br>  makehelp.exe        help compiler<br>  *.txt               text files describing the various B-Tree<br>                      Filer units<br><br>NET disk (supplied only with Network version of B-Tree Filer)<br>----------------<br>netbonus.lzh      - BONUS NetWare function calls<br>netinfo.exe       - precompiled version of netinfo demonstration<br>                    program<br>nreceive.exe      - precompiled version of nreceive demonstration<br>                    program<br>nsend.exe         - precompiled version of nsend demonstration<br>                    program<br>netfiler.lzh      - archive containing B-Tree Filer network<br>                    source code<br>  ipxspx.asm          assembly language for ipxspx.obj<br>  ipxspx.inc            included in netware.pas<br>  ipxspx.obj            linked into netware.pas<br>  ixpspxd.pas         IPX/SPX access DLL for Windows<br>  isamnwrk.inc          included in filer.pas<br>  isnetsup.inc          included in filer.pas<br>  mesexamp.pas        NetWare and NetBIOS message demonstration<br>                      program<br>  nbchatw.pas         NetBIOS chat demonstration program for<br>                      Windows<br>  netbios.inc           included in netbios.pas<br>  netbiosw.inc          included in netbios.pas<br>  netbios.pas         NetBIOS access unit<br>  netbiosd.pas        NetBIOS access DLL for Windows<br>  netexamp.pas        network fileblock example routines<br>  netfiler.mak        make file for network B-Tree Filer<br>  netinfo.pas         NetWare and NetBIOS service demonstration<br>                      program<br>  netsema.pas         used by netdemo.pas<br>  netware.inc           included in netware.pas<br>  netware.pas         NetWare access unit<br>  netwarew.inc          included in netware.pas<br>  nreceive.pas        network file transfer demonstration program<br>                      - receiving<br>  nreceivw.pas        network file transfer demo for Windows<br>  nsend.pas           network file transfer demonstration program<br>                      - sending<br>  nsendw.pas          network file transfer demo for Windows<br>  share.inc             included in share.pas<br>  sharew.inc            included in share.pas<br>  share.pas           DOS 3.x SHARE access unit<br>  windpmi.pas         Windows DPMI access unit<br><br>BONUS disk<br>----------------<br>read.me!          - file describing bonus files<br>extend.lzh        - increase number of file handles even for DOS<br>                    &lt;3.3<br>fbrowse.lzh       - object-oriented fileblock browser for use<br>                    with OPRO<br>lharcman.lzh      - documentation for LHARC.EXE<br>netbios.lzh       - miscellaneous NetBIOS functions<br>netprn.lzh        - NetWare print queue management<br>nettest.lzh       - network messaging tests<br>obrowse.lzh       - OOP fileblock browsers for Windows/TV/OPRO<br>oofiler.lzh       - fileblock management objects<br>prealloc.lzh      - data and index file preallocation unit<br>reindex.lzh       - fileblock reindexing units<br>traffic.lzh       - test network loading with fileblock operations<br>winsort.lzh       - sorting demo program for Windows</pre>|btf5_40.zip|1080928|17.11.1992|17.11.1992|213.189.205.12|tv-sq.tver.fact400.ru|vot
